article.headline: Fort has 16 in Samford's 86-65 victory over West Georgia
article.description: — Trey Fort's 16 points helped Samford defeat West Georgia 86-65 on Friday night.
article.linkText: Fort has 16 in Samford's 86-65 victory over West Georgia
article.story: BIRMINGHAM, Ala. -- — Trey Fort's 16 points helped Samford defeat West Georgia 86-65 on Friday night. Fort went 6 of 16 from the field (3 for 8 from 3-point range) for the Bulldogs (7-2). Josh Holloway added 13 points while going 5 of 6 (3 for 4 from 3-point range) to go with six assists. The Wolves (0-9) were led in scoring by Shelton Williams-Dryden, who finished with 21 points, 13 rebounds and three steals. Kolten Griffin added nine points, six rebounds and four steals for West Georgia. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
